parameters: \n<Apprentice>It seems to be a package from Dr. Marion.
\n<Streamer>Probably just press here to open it.
\n<New model sexaroid>I am the new model sexaroid, \C[24]Eroli-\C[0].
\n<Apprentice>Does that mean you're the second one?

\n<New model sexaroid>No, the previous model was destroyed during transport. I am
the first of the new models.
\n<New model sexaroid>\C[24]Eury\C[0] is the name of a modified girl, right.
\n<New model sexaroid>\C[2]There is no sexaroid with the same name.
\n<Mister>Ahaha. I just remembered something I have to do.
\n<Streamer>Alright! Let's get pumped up for Tengen TV today too!

\n<Eury>Everyone! I've taken care of all the monsters around
Tengen Town!
\n<Eury>In front of the modified girl, evil has been vanquished!
\n<Mister>I believed in you from the start!
\n<Streamer>Eury-chan is the strongest modi... modified girl after all!
\n<New model sexaroid>As expected of you, Eury-san.
\n<Eury>Ehehe. It's embarrassing to be praised like this.

\n<Eury>There's been a lot happening in this town, but soon I'll
start my activities at the next base!

\n<Eury>Let's work hard to return this town to the peaceful place it
was before the monster troubles!
\n<New model sexaroid>There's just one thing I want to ask...
